OL,3,CBoy who died in lake 'could not swim',
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FA teenager who is thought to have
OL,7,Fdrowned in a lake during the recent
OL,8,Fheatwave could not swim, an inquest
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FThe body of 16-year-old Muhammed Secka
OL,12,Fwas found the day after emergency
OL,13,Fservices were called to Rother Valley
OL,14,FCountry Park, in South Yorkshire, on
OL,15,FBank Holiday Monday.
OL,17,FHe is one of at least 15 people who
OL,18,Fdied after getting into trouble in
OL,19,Fopen water during the hot spell.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
