PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781201470
OL,3,CBoy who died in lake 'could not swim',
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FAn inquest into Muhammed's death was
OL,7,Fopened and adjourned by Rotherham's
OL,8,Fsenior coroner Nicola Mundy at
OL,9,FDoncaster Coroner's Court on Tuesday.
OL,11,FCoroner's officer Siobhan Golightly
OL,12,Ftold the brief hearing that Muhammed
OL,13,Fhad gone to the country park with
OL,14,Ffriends on Monday 25 May.
OL,16,FMs Golightly said: "At approximately
OL,17,F7pm he had been in the water with
OL,18,Ffriends when he disappeared from view.
OL,20,F"The alarm was raised and the
OL,21,Femergency services were contacted."
OL,26,@xD@TOU|D@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
