PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781201470
OL,3,CBoy who died in lake 'could not swim',
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FShe said Muhammed's body was located
OL,7,Fin the water in the early hours of the
OL,8,Ffollowing day and he was pronounced
OL,9,Fdead by paramedics at the scene.
OL,11,FMs Golightly said: "It's reported that
OL,12,FMuhammed was not able to swim."
OL,14,FThe coroner said a post-mortem
OL,15,Fexamination showed "features in
OL,16,Fkeeping with drowning".
OL,18,FBut she said that was only a
OL,19,Fpreliminary conclusion and was subject
OL,20,Fto further investigations.
OL,26,@sD@TOUtD@_O]wD@TOUxD@VO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
