OL,3,CBoy who died in lake 'could not swim',
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FShe adjourned the inquest to date to
OL,7,Fbe fixed.
OL,9,FNo family members were present for the
OL,10,Fhearing.
OL,12,FFriends of Muhammed and his family
OL,13,Fstarted online fundraising campaigns
OL,14,Ffollowing his death.
OL,16,FOne organiser said: "Muhammed was a
OL,17,Fmuch-loved son, friend, student and
OL,18,Fmember of the community who brought
OL,19,Flight, laughter and kindness to those
OL,20,Faround him.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
