PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781201470
OL,3,CBoy who died in lake 'could not swim',
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,F"His loss has deeply affected everyone
OL,7,Fwho knew him, and the pain felt by his
OL,8,Ffamily and loved ones is unimaginable."
OL,10,FMuhammed's death, along with a number
OL,11,Fof others over the last few weeks, has
OL,12,Fprompted pleas from the emergency
OL,13,Fservices, families and campaigners for
OL,14,Fyoungsters to stay away from open
OL,15,Fwater, which can be treacherous.
OL,17,FHe was one of at least 17 people to
OL,18,Fhave lost their lives in similar
OL,19,Fcircumstances in recent weeks,
OL,20,Fincluding several in the Calendar
OL,21,Fregion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@gO]
