OL,3,CBoy who died in lake 'could not swim',
OL,4,Cinquest told
OL,6,FDeclan Sawyer, 15, died after an
OL,7,Fincident at Swanholme Lakes in
OL,8,FLincolnshire; 13-year-old Reco Puttock
OL,9,Fdied at Leadbeater Dam in West
OL,10,FYorkshire; Mackenzie Swift, 11, lost
OL,11,Fhis life in the River Don, near
OL,12,FMexborough; Palwasha Akbar, 13, died
OL,13,Fafter being pulled from the River
OL,14,FWharfe near Burnsall in the Skipton
OL,15,Farea; and Panashe Muchenje, 19, died
OL,16,Fat Balderton Lake near Newark.
